Module kivakit.primitive.collections
Package com.telenav.kivakit.primitive.collections.list

Interface PrimitiveList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.interfaces.numeric.Countable, com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.interfaces.numeric.Sized
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ByteList, CharList, IntList, LongList, ShortList
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteArray, CharArray, IntArray, LongArray, PackedArray, ShortArray, SplitByteArray, SplitCharArray, SplitIntArray, SplitLongArray, SplitPackedArray
    public interface PrimitiveList
extends com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.interfaces.numeric.Sized
    Interface implemented by primitive lists. Primitive values are treated as longs to unify the different lists and allow them to be treated the same.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    ByteList, IntList, LongList, ShortList
